name: Personal Jesus
description:
"...
Feeling unknown
And you're all alone
Flesh and bone
By the telephone
Lift up the receiver
I'll make you a believer
I will deliver
You know I'm a forgiver

Reach out and touch faith

Your own personal Jesus
..."

---------


My woodcut drop for 5OOK objkts minted on Hen. Very straight and rough carving, printed on paper & on fabric with a wooden spoon. 

It will be my last mint of a woodcut for a moment.
